data.description: Indulge in the captivating charm of this meticulously maintained dwelling featuring a revitalizing pool! Upon entry, the well-crafted enhancements immediately captivate your attention. The focal point is the saltwater pool from 2020, showcasing a stylish Stonescape finish in a custom color with a Lifetime warranty.Step inside to discover the 2020 addition of a generator hookup for added convenience, while security is enhanced by a new roof installed in 2021 and hurricane impact windows from 2022. Exceptional energy efficiency is achieved with 16" blown insulation in the attic and a brand-new exterior AC unit in 2023. Preserving the serenity of your backyard oasis, a new privacy fence surrounds the property, complemented by lush landscaping. Strategically positioned in a non-flood zone, this gem provides peace of mind and security. With major updates already addressed, this home ensures a move-in-ready experience. As a bonus, the property includes a 7.5 x 14 ft. shed in the backyard! Seize the opportunity to make this haven your own.The sellers is offering a home warranty that includes, covering all pool equipment and​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ more!
